short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Tools of diagnostication and customization for NSP device.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
NSP device development supporting tool set. These tools are
1. NSP device console.
2. Program and configuration editor.
3. NSP to host downloader.
4. Host to NSP uploader.
5. NSP development documents.
